The '''Unu''' was the lead nest of all of the [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] nests. It was headed by a group of joint Killiks/[[Joiner]]s from each nest that were in turn led by [[Raynar Thul]] (UnuThul). This nest was known as the conscience of all the other nests, but in reality, the Unu was controlled by the [[Gorog]], or the Dark Nest. Some also served as UnuThul's bodyguards, but they were killed when [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] confronted Raynar and [[Lomi Plo]] above [[Tenupe]].

